narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned about concepts in physics (specifically electricity and magnetism topics) through experiments and corresponding data collection.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: With a different professor or TA, yes.

Due to the accelerated nature of this course, I would only recommend taking this course out of necessity, to fulfill a requirement. It is more likely that a students ability to learn and digest the content would occur if the class were taken for a full semester.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
How will you use the knowledge and skills you learned in this course in your future endeavors?
comments: A lot of my understanding of electronics (from taking this course) will be applicable to daily life, as well as professionally. I also think that the abilities to analyze and read critically will be useful in a broad sense, particularly in a career in medicine and/or research.
